==English==

=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /"pVn/
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /'p ån/

=== Noun ===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A [[joke]] made by confusing two similarly pronounced words or phrases.

==== Examples ====
Note: Because puns are based on pronunciation, puns are often more obvious when spoken aloud.

"This rock is [[w:gneiss|gneiss]], but don't take it for [[w:granite|granite]]." (This rock is nice, but don't take it for granted.)

